text: Hyperbaena is a genus of plants in family Menispermaceae. ==Species== Illustration of Hyperbaena domingensis (Orig. Pérez & Cast.-Campos *Hyperbaena laurifolia *Hyperbaena eptobotryosa *Hyperbaena lindmanii *Hyperbaena mexicana *Hyperbaena oblongifolia *Hyperbaena prioriana Miers *Hyperbaena smilacina *Hyperbaena standleyi *Hyperbaena tonduzii *Hyperbaena undulata *Hyperbaena winzerlingii *Hyperbaena valida Miers ==References== Category:Menispermaceae Category:Menispermaceae genera Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
